channel.title: [REL] Downscape 317
channel.description:
[center]Hello people first of all i dit not want to release this its based on hybrid pvp but i had because me co-owner deleted the server of the vps stil had a backup so im releasing it first of all its based on hybrid pvp v3 i fixed loads of bugs i only got the last screens from server page : [img]http://i56.tinypic.com/2evfclu.gif[/img] [img]https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-P64NO3idvik/TdbpdQWR67I/AAAAAAAAACo/ciH8FJ_33pk/rush.gif[/img] [img]https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-1pNl4HsJE5E/TdgJHXNEzUI/AAAAAAAAAC4/8kGNGInt36Q/Untitled.gif[/img] [img]https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-G9-p32uhM3M/TdUJbQKRwJI/AAAAAAAAADs/L4z9_KeKZss/Untitled.gif[/img] [img]https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-d2wt4hfzeek/TdUGiMv-EXI/AAAAAAAAADk/UQQj3zFYkMI/Untitled.gif[/img] [img]https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-F1HIacItP8s/TdT70KPXe4I/AAAAAAAAADU/4tx_wcf47VY/shields.gif[/img]
it also has summoning system does work titan does attack and pack yak and other works 100% custom home ect. screen : [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/taq7eu.png[/img]
you can only have 2 starter packs on 1 ip 100% trade logs and most of all dupes fixed. portal at home is for dungeoneering. for dungeoneering watch this video lots of updates have been made its already updated bosses items and allot more so try it out : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MtAd_Ix4OCU
Dont say its leached cos the base is hybrid pvp and i give credit for that awesome source. i fixed many problems try it out Ur self i added dungeoneering base to it written by me easy base but good to start with eh you can delete voting stuff it has like voting shop voting skill and voting points system u can easely delete those idk what to say dont flame this topic or il delete the stuff.
download client : [url=http://uppit.com/p1n7ih4juhxf/Client.rar]Hybrid pvp client v3[/url] download server : [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?3at68uv5ngg8qlb]Download server here[/url] Downscape original client with anti leach : [url=http://uppit.com/c41ira5wdage/Downscape_Dungeoneering.rar]here[/url][/center]
credits : Hybrid pvp 25% for client and server for what is left :P Justhin 75% for editing stuff and adding alot.
